0723,"uid":80036,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"59c45a6fb5d935ba48759b86a49becc0a036e2ae","tid":1450723,"uid":80036,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"41b1a7f55166e23e80297d43693ba98516d5adf3","tid":1450723,"uid":231103,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:10:06.000Z","msg":"我真心諗左好耐我嘅推論，我係發覺依兩個月個運動開始失焦，係林奠走出尼撥番大個火。<br />\n<br />\nMK 輝講過，政府自運動開始以來，每個動作都係完美嘅 failure。<br />\n<br />\n大家要識做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:43.000Z","msg":"每次記者會佢用不屑嘅眼神望大家。<br />\n其實係一種對我哋唔生性嘅不滿，又要我出尼做野嘅態度。<br />\n如果大家用依個角度思考會唔會容易理解啲？"},{"pid":"33628ef24c0cc736daa96177f6999e836d3a8f56","tid":1450723,"uid":80036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:37:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7af0a56f3229cf5ed540d11ccc1b71647242ada8","tid":1450723,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:41:04.000Z","msg":"匪共無起疑咩？"},{"pid":"39e3c8bc612b213cf15debafc4ff558700548d6d","tid":1450723,"uid":80036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7af0a56f3229cf5ed540d11ccc1b71647242ada8","tid":1450723,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:41:04.000Z","msg":"匪共無起疑咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:51:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/453539841327141/posts/2782228088458293/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F453539841327141%2Fposts%2F2782228088458293%2F&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=bebde957\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/453539841327141/posts/2782228088458293/</a><br />\n<br />\n係因為互相利用緊，兩邊都似玩緊火，不過係睇下幾時燒死哂所有人，到最後冇死嗰個就係王。<br />\n<br />\n習仔會諗高手過招，有意思有意思。<br />\n<br />\n所有希望大家做啲真正幫到手，對準極權嘅野。依家打機卡關呀，打極都見唔到大佬呀"},{"pid":"5567d570627482c862687e6b8f084082ad788687","tid":1450723,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:04:37.000Z","msg":"我再陰謀d 成個都係劇本<br />\n<br />\n咁岩中美大戰 今年就反送中<br />\n咁岩g20就黎612<br />\n咁岩台灣選總統就黎個一國兩制示範<br />\n<br />\n希望我係被迫害妄想。。。"}]}